        "data": {
          "comment": "# 📖 Wikipedia Agent\n\nGive a seed URL and topic; the agent researches and writes a Wikipedia-style article in markdown.\n\n**Pipeline:** Seed URL + topic → build prompt → research agent\n\n**Try this:** point it at any topic or change the article style."
